{"tid":2923,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"魔法少女伊莉亞-46話","createTime":"2016-11-26T03:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T16:17:02.000Z","uid":7307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"658d40a0cd765fb5ed5d5ebc8aab8365f314adc5","tid":2923,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/114421_ab26c328b7559595d5d996a4b1495661.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F114421_ab26c328b7559595d5d996a4b1495661.jpg&h=9fdecd38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/114422_9ed8c8cb3ce4bfb585b7427e388b2ebc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F114422_9ed8c8cb3ce4bfb585b7427e388b2ebc.jpg&h=907319f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到黑伊同士郎哥段對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個感覺好似hf線呢段<br />\n<br />\n「不可能的。我既活不長久，士郎也無法活太久的。所以，我們無法生活在一起。」<br />\n「或許某一方為另一方犧牲的话，還能再多活一些時間也說不定。但是我想，要兩個人都在一起實在太勉強。當這場戰爭結束後，如果我活著，那就表示士郎已经不在了。」<br />\n「你瞧，所以不可能實現。因為没有士郎在的衛宮家，就無法成為我的住處。」"},{"pid":"e8590a019d7d8a77a807c20e069f00705d99123b","tid":2923,"uid":25985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T19:12:50.000Z","msg":"下集係唔係要挖番切J爸爸條屍黎整起源彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb46b75b9b093096fc5e5881449c2e8e1959ac3","tid":2923,"uid":2674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T19:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下集係唔係要挖番切J爸爸條屍黎整起源彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起源彈有66粒，切𠻸fate zero前都淨係用左37粒<br />\n呢邊冇打過聖杯戰爭，應該起碼有29粒用"},{"pid